import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useParams, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import "../Home/home.css"; import "../Product/product.css"; import axios from 'axios'; // import logout from "../Functions/logout"; function Product() { const {id} = useParams(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const [data, setData] = useState({name : ""}); const [username, setUsername] = useState(); function logout(){ localStorage.removeItem('token'); navigate('/login'); } useEffect(()=>{ console.log(id); const token = localStorage.getItem('token'); axios.get( `http://localhost:5000/product/${id}`, { headers : { Authorization: token, }}).then(async (res) =>{ setUsername(res.data.user.username) console.log(res.data); setData(res.data); console.log(res.data.item.name); }) .catch((error) => { // console.log(error); navigate('/login'); }); },[]); return
